        protected AbstractFeatureBean(Id owner,

        Parameters:
        owner - the identifier of the object using the feature
        id - the identifier of the feature of the owner
        position - the position of the feature
        Throws:
        NullPointerException - if any argument is null
        IllegalArgumentException - if the position is negative when isMany() == true
